#   "ollama:llama3.2"          ← default & preferred (local, free)
#   "openai:gpt-4o"            ← OpenAI
#   "google_genai:gemini-2.5-flash"   ← Gemini (fast & cheap)
#   "anthropic:claude-3-5-sonnet-latest" ← Claude
#   "groq:llama-3.3-70b"       ← Groq (very fast)
